      <title>特朗普将在 CEO 活动前与参议院共和党人会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/trump-to-meet-with-senate-republicans-before-ceo-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将于周四会见参议院共和党人，这是华盛顿决策者为制定前总统赢得第二任期后的优先事项所做的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/trump-to-meet-with-senate-republicans-before-ceo-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 22:18:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥官员称海外投票可能需要更多预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/mexico-voting-abroad-may-require-bigger-budget-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责该过程的官员表示，未来的墨西哥选举可能需要更大的预算，以避免公民在今年总统选举中遇到的海外投票问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/mexico-voting-abroad-may-require-bigger-budget-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 22:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国法官警告香港法治“严重受损”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/top-hong-kong-court-loses-third-overseas-judge-as-scrutiny-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，一位从香港最高法院辞职的英国著名法官对中国打压异见人士的做法提出了严厉批评，警告称，香港这个金融中心的法治面临“严重危险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/top-hong-kong-court-loses-third-overseas-judge-as-scrutiny-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 18:39:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克因英国减税宣言面临保守党的强烈反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/sunak-faces-last-ditch-tory-revolt-over-uk-election-manifesto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党宣言的早期草案引发了外界不安，人们担心该宣言缺乏可能避免保守党在英国大选中惨败的重大承诺。内阁大臣们在最后一刻呼吁里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在宣言中添加新的减税措施和更严格的移民政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/sunak-faces-last-ditch-tory-revolt-over-uk-election-manifesto</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:49:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将接受纽约缓刑官员的线上面试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/trump-to-be-interviewed-by-probation-officers-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普周一接受了纽约缓刑官的讯问，该缓刑官的量刑报告将帮助法官决定这位前总统因伪造商业记录将在监狱中服刑多长时间（如果有的话）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/trump-to-be-interviewed-by-probation-officers-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 04:08:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
